Tivoli is a cooperative musical project between two generations. The music is created by:



Ossian Bor&eacute;n komponerar, mixar och producerar musik. Han studerar bild och form p&aring; Schillerska Gymnasiet i G&ouml;teborg. &Auml;r Intresserad av konst och design, samt sysslar med webbdesign.

Ossian Bor&eacute;n compose, mix and produce music. He studies art and form at Schillerska Gymnasiet in Gothenbourg, Sweden. Interested in art and design, web design as well.



Petra Bor&eacute;n komponerar musik, skriver texter och sjunger i Tivoli. Hon arbetar som bildkonstn&auml;r, med atelj&eacute; p&aring; Konstepidemin i G&ouml;teborg. Hon har l&auml;nge jobbat med musik ihop med bild.

Petra Bor&eacute;n compose music, writes lyrics and makes all the vocals for Tivoli. She works as an artist, with a studio at Konstepidemin in Gothenbourg, Sweden. She has combined image and music in her works for several years.
